15.0– 15.5; length of hind femur: 
<specimenCount box="[461,482,1591,1617]" pageId="7" pageNumber="190" type="male">♂</specimenCount>
5.4–6.0, 
<specimenCount box="[587,608,1591,1617]" pageId="7" pageNumber="190" type="female">♀</specimenCount>
6.5–7.0.
</paragraph>
