<taxonomicName authorityName="Deng" authorityYear="2022" box="[759,930,1870,1896]" class="Insecta" family="Tetrigidae" genus="Xistra" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="9" pageNumber="192" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="nigriabdominis">
<emphasis box="[759,930,1870,1896]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="192">nigriabdominis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
”, meaning Sternites of abdomen is black. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,353,1906,1932]" pageId="9" pageNumber="192">Distribution.</emphasis>
P. R. 
<collectingCountry box="[419,512,1907,1933]" name="China" pageId="9" pageNumber="192">CHINA</collectingCountry>
: 
<collectingRegion box="[522,616,1906,1932]" country="China" name="Sichuan" pageId="9" pageNumber="192">Sichuan</collectingRegion>
.
</paragraph>
